# Spectrum â€” frequency band visualizer
# Three concentric rings, each driven by a different audio band.
# Bass (gold/orange inner), Mid (cyan middle), Treble (violet outer).
# Drop audio to see each frequency band light up independently.

cinematic "Spectrum" {
  layer {
    fn: spectrum(bass, mid, treble)
    bass: 0.0 ~ audio.bass * 1.5
    mid: 0.0 ~ audio.mid * 1.5
    treble: 0.0 ~ audio.treble * 1.5
  }
}
